---
title: Sloppy Jose Pulled Chicken and Cheese Burger with Potato Wedges, Guacamole and Fresh Tomato Salsa
description: We love good Chicken with Wedges and Guac and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sloppy-chicken-jose-6c2aa514-d66aa47d.jpg
